text: Henrik Ohlmeyer (born 11 February 1946) is a German ski jumper. He competed in the normal hill and large hill events at the 1968 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1946 births Category:Living people Category:German male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of West Germany Category:Ski jumpers at the 1968 Winter Olympics Category:People from Bayreuth (district)
title: Henrik Ohlmeyer
